{"tid":1653750,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"保方享受和謙虛的C朗合作","createTime":"2019-10-14T08:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T08:29:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa1429512f5a3985825fafa86d197d0ef1f21b4","tid":1653750,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"保方今季重返祖雲達斯和C朗拿度合作，他說自己發掘了謙虛的C朗，很享受和他合作。<br />\n<br />\n保方說重返祖記，見識到C朗的幽默感和態度，令他感到非常有趣。<br />\n<br />\n「我在訓練時見到非常謙虛的C朗，他的態度以及和隊友的相處令我欣賞。很多時候，大家在訓練之後都會恭時間再深入討論，我發現這位足球員的親切一面。」保方接受訪問時說道。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=a09e9120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"12eed9e9cf072f9430fcc77f478b154ffec9c45f","tid":1653750,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:29:56.000Z","msg":"今時今日的保方=廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}